note right of TenantContext
  ThreadLocal storage for
  current organization ID.
  Set by TenantFilter on
  each HTTP request.
end note

note right of TenantFilter
  Intercepts HTTP requests.
  Detects authenticated user.
  Sets organization context.
  Clears context after request.
end note

note right of OrganizationService
  Manages organizations,
  validates plan limits,
  controls resource quotas.
end note

